      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project car or a reliable source of parts. The body shows significant signs of age and neglect, including several deep dents, visible rust along the wheel wells, and a heavily faded paint job. Mechanically, the car requires major attention; the engine runs roughly, and the transmission is showing signs of slippage. The interior is also in need of a complete overhaul, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please come prepared with a trailer, as it is not currently in road-worthy condition.",
