      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the mechanical connection is unparalleled. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from M-specific subframe geometry and a functional M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the high-pressure VANOS system is quiet, and the rod bearings have been proactively addressed. Braking performance is sharp via cross-drilled rotors and multi-piston calipers. A purist\u2019s spec featuring the factory carbon fiber roof to lower the center of gravity, this machine is mechanically robust and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 32500.0,
